00:17:37,190 --> 00:17:41,070
And as we just said, we did not
enable traffic through HTTPS.

401
00:17:41,070 --> 00:17:44,027
The default port, I
think, is 443 for that.

402
00:17:44,027 --> 00:17:45,860
And we also have it
enabled the certificate,

