00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:42,160
So that's why I'm doing sudo rm.

441
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:49,045
Now, I'm going to do
sudo nano index.html.

442
00:19:49,045 --> 00:19:50,170
The reason I'm doing sudo--

