445
00:19:52,880 --> 00:19:54,770
It didn't matter because
I didn't edit the file.

446
00:19:54,770 --> 00:19:56,320
But if I tried to edit
and save the file,

447
00:19:56,320 --> 00:19:57,490
it would have thrown
an error because I

