edit the file as just my user

449
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:00,300
account.

450
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:02,840
So again, need root
level permissions.

451
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:04,750
I'm going to edit the file.

452
00:20:04,750 --> 00:20:05,863
And now, it's blank.

